Concept: If there is ony one character then there will be 26 numbers for column from A-Z.

Now if we use two characters for column then there will be also 26 numbers like AA-AZ. And we have to add previous 26 numbers to this to find final column.

So we have to multiply the result every time by 26 upto the length of our string given.

Ex. Input : ABC

