The whole game revolves around the number 26( (26 alphabets) and powers of 26(Depends on the lenth of string).
Example:

A = 1
AA = 26\*1 + 1
AAA = 26\*26\*1 + 26\*1 + 1
.........
Overall ```Formula: 26*(l-1)*x + 26*(l-2)*x + .... + 26*x + x```
Where, L = length of string
			x = Numerical value of that particular letter(```columnTitle[i]```) of the string. 
```
int titleToNumber(string columnTitle) {
       //columnTitle

        int l = columnTitle.length();

        //We'll have to keep a note regarding powers of 26.
        int it = l-1;

        //storing result
        long long int sum = 0;

        for(int i = 0;i<l;i++)
        {
            int curr = columnTitle[i]-'A';
            curr+=1; //A=1, not 0

            curr = pow(26,it)*curr;

            sum = sum+curr;
            it--;
        }

        return sum;
    }
```

