**Idea:** [Half Adder](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adder_(electronics)#Half_adder)
* Using HA logic, add a and b bitwise
* sum(a, b) = a `XOR` b and carry generated = a `AND` b
* Add this sum to the carry to get the total sum.
* Do this recursively till carry reduces to 0
> **T/S:** O(1)/O(1)

**Variation 1:** Recursive
```
public int getSum(int a, int b) {
	return (b == 0) ? a : getSum(a ^ b, (a & b) << 1);
}
```

**Variation 2:** Iterative
```
public int getSum(int a, int b) {
	while (b != 0) {
		var carry = a & b;
		a ^= b;
		b = carry << 1;
	}
	return a;
}
```
