# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
the top view project required a simple count of blocks
the x projection finds the largest number in each subarray of the grid array
the y projection finds the largest number throughout all subarrays for that index and creates a new array. Then this array's sum is returned.

