Algorithm:
1. Traversing the vector array from last and continuously adding the last element of integer 'K'
	a. Adding k to num[i]
	b. Updating k by num[i]/10
	b. Updating num[i] by num[i]%10  
2. If any carry left, it will be inserted at start of the vector array num
3. Return the array.

Time Complexity: O(n)
Space Complexity: O(1)

