# Approach
We are taking carry. We start from the last digit in array num add carry and the modulus of the input k%10.
Then update array and move untill the highest digit.
After traversing array if carry is > 0 then we add it to begining of num vector using a loop
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->

# Complexity

- Time complexity: $$O(n)$$

In this problem k is at most 5 digits 
So, Insertion time complexity doesn't matter

- Space complexity: $$O(1)$$

# Code
```
class Solution {
public:
    vector<int> addToArrayForm(vector<int>& num, int a) {
        ios_base::sync_with_stdio(false);
        cin.tie(NULL);        
        int carry=0;
        for(int i=num.size()-1;i>=0;i--) {
            num[i]=(num[i]+(a%10)) +carry;
            carry = num[i]/10;            
            num[i]=num[i]%10;
            a=a/10;
        }        
        if(carry!=0 || a!=0) {
            carry=carry+a;
            while(carry !=0) {
                num.insert(num.begin(),carry%10);
                carry/=10;    
            }       
        }            
        return num;
    }
};
```
